{"tid":1095481,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"食飯唔夠錢比,佢話我係廢物","createTime":"2019-04-07T05:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T01:28:34.000Z","uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"a61d5623108c9af182ba86bdbfc7c3e89464a67f","tid":1095481,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:02:04.000Z","msg":"我同女友係中學同學，不過佢留過兩年班，所以大我兩年，拍左兩年拖，大家係彼此初戀。上年我升大學，佢grad中學就岀黎做野。初時冇乜野，但近排佢越發越多脾氣。例如我有時約左佢，遲左5分鐘到，佢一嬲可以嬲成個星期，仲要我買手袋手鍊氹返佢。如果唔買，佢就keep住鬧我，話拍拖係任何時候都氹人，唔識玩呢個遊戲就死開。(exact wordings，死開)<br />\n<br />\n佢發脾氣既內容都好多姿多采：前幾日落雨佢冇帶遮，佢發我三日脾氣，話我唔提佢；我阿爸阿媽放假喺屋企，佢唔方便上我到，又嬲返我三兩日；佢放工走左班車，我咁岩send咗whatsapp俾佢，佢賴我阻住佢上車。<br />\n<br />\n有次我病到入院，我通知佢我喺邊間病房，佢冇關心之餘仲嫌我身體差，仲同我講：「你病唔關我事。點解咁多人身體咁強壯咁大隻你唔係？其他人身體孱，至少佢地會好快死，仲會留遺產俾屋企人。但你又要孱又要唔死，死你啲錢又俾唔到我，咁你個身體孱嚟有乜意義？」 佢周不時都呻返工辛苦，要我都quit 大學岀黎做野，儲錢結婚。我冇辦法quit 大學，佢就嬲我，我唯有做酒吧，一放學就去返酒吧由夜晚10點返到朝早6點，一個月終於賺五六千。但我有工就要交家用，交完得三千，搞自己洗費之餘，女友要我拍拖食飯都係我俾錢，或者俾大數，佢俾零頭。<br />\n<br />\n有幾次真係好hurt，有個月考試冇乜返工，嗰個月月入只有二千，所以月尾冇乜錢同佢岀街。點知佢話：「冇錢唔該唔好學人拍拖，點解我會識著你呢個廢人」。佢嬲咗我成個星期，我唯有同屋企人借啲錢，bk枱同佢食左餐埋單四千幾嘅日本野。<br />\n<br />\n另一次，我淨係帶左五百岀街，冇帶卡，同佢行街。突然佢要我請佢食outback，我又唔夠錢俾晒，佢睥咗我一眼，講咗句：「廢物」，然後就自己走咗。<br />\n<br />\n發我脾氣，可以，但真係越嚟越氣餒，不斷對佢好，但佢不留情面話我，我都越嚟越冇心機氹佢。嫌我窮，可以，事實我岀身唔好，阿爸破過產，仲有斷左腳唔返得工，得阿媽做野，但唔知點解要鬧我鬧得咁苛刻咁衝動。<br />\n<br />\n唔知一直以嚟係我太理性，定係太感性。知佢或者因為工作壓力大，同埋唔多唔少價值觀同我有D岀入，所以我堅持要自己忍佢，唔忍就係我理虧；另一方面，真係太愛佢，我寧願忍佢氣。"},{"pid":"00d774487cb1faf021e228d8dcb2fb60b1581ead","tid":1095481,"uid":12417,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:06:21.000Z","msg":"too long doesnt read<br />\n不過話得你廢物如果你唔係真係好撚廢既話就飛得"},{"pid":"9ba1f9e2a687854f022d0353dd7192fbbf2d4ef3","tid":1095481,"uid":161352,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"做人做狗自己諗<br />\n中出即飛 好黎好去"},{"pid":"25bc1da4ecd94eae56c8f25cf09dc7c180f942b8","tid":1095481,"uid":87757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"有無得上先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a43266568b07f9d1cfd29c4ae6366abe240e63","tid":1095481,"uid":181063,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:07:21.000Z","msg":"認真，佢愛錢多過愛你。<br />\n大學一定唔quit. 有證書好過無。 係講緊真係大學非大專。<br />\n呢啲女人，早飛早著。 你會開心好多，唔好比兩年時間嘅感情束縛你。 我之前3年，都係咁講分手，初時好痛，但認真講句 對自己好啲吧。<br />\n分手後會發現呢個世界多姿多彩！"},{"pid":"f06e9640ff927916d0649c65057fe0b38123a92a","tid":1095481,"uid":29080,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"又真係幾廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485b6f50e1f8e23be38334c8d5c95ea618a3c246","tid":1095481,"uid":137743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"佢真係你女朋友？"},{"pid":"0c2e5c6a4a397523140c62a165bd6f25e8e26bf3","tid":1095481,"uid":47080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"你女友腥港人嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算啦，你都清楚佢睇錢多過睇你，搵過第2個啦"},{"pid":"c1553526be08a751b68094abe5f63fd8633149d1","tid":1095481,"uid":47080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"485b6f50e1f8e23be38334c8d5c95ea618a3c246","tid":1095481,"uid":137743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"佢真係你女朋友？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:10:40.000Z","msg":"你又岩喎！似係兵啊"},{"pid":"afd8d95f4e91fbd5faca00255e60117ca576c44f","tid":1095481,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"25bc1da4ecd94eae56c8f25cf09dc7c180f942b8","tid":1095481,"uid":87757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"有無得上先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n佢話唔鍾意搞呢D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574b43b55a4921a16f71dac2368131b39cb4fb17","tid":1095481,"uid":143344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"唔分手對唔對得住自己啊？"},{"pid":"01d3f1afb25233852466d697fb93add0eefdc2fe","tid":1095481,"uid":11909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"佢有返工點解佢唔比錢？<br />\n唔係話要計得清清楚楚，除二仲要計到小數位後兩個位個種，但兩個人一齊大家都要付出"},{"pid":"3c487034dd0a480681172c44f32f03b7412385a5","tid":1095481,"uid":190714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"afd8d95f4e91fbd5faca00255e60117ca576c44f","tid":1095481,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"25bc1da4ecd94eae56c8f25cf09dc7c180f942b8","tid":1095481,"uid":87757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"有無得上先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n佢話唔鍾意搞呢D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:14:27.000Z","msg":"此po已完"},{"pid":"32a7916e338d578e4feed1faf09170588c13ef87","tid":1095481,"uid":190144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:14:54.000Z","msg":"分手啦 條女愛錢多過你 呢啲女唔可以過世架 玩又唔玩得 要黎做乜"},{"pid":"7dcca4c69b79b2f2428c8e3c3d54ef6000d79e10","tid":1095481,"uid":234086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"分啦，一睇就知條女有第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c9305c80bbddffadc9dade0b17972ae66db9d2","tid":1095481,"uid":26573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:15:53.000Z","msg":"佢自卑所以要貶低你價值 早走早著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2873318e4fb103b676efeb670de6696c11c3859","tid":1095481,"uid":45999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:17:19.000Z","msg":"咁你都忍到？"},{"pid":"013b5c5871e84e76cc672cd8d6b37f80c9858301","tid":1095481,"uid":41157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:17:48.000Z","msg":"佢冇講錯<br />\n咁你都仲忍<br />\n你真係廢物"},{"pid":"b79d273d5c54cec3e2055a1f33b1b23d07a338bd","tid":1095481,"uid":55859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447ef29637202333c7aceb63b54220a6c49c1273","tid":1095481,"uid":59848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"你的確係廢物 咁嘅女都唔飛 on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係條女真係靚到天上有地下無<br />\n咁你可以放上嚟比各位巴絲評鑑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62765d3f2fc256711987149e9d719775d6458690","tid":1095481,"uid":47819,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:19:39.000Z","msg":"女仔本身就早熟<br />\n仲要早番工過你<br />\n知道錢緊要<br />\n而你又少少都冇咁濟<br />\n真係好難搞<br />\n分吧啦<br />\n時間上唔夾<br />\n一齊盞大家辛苦"},{"pid":"f9f5f47284ae4123f4568d992f7a391bb6a2ee68","tid":1095481,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"佢無話錯你 你真係廢物 俾條女食住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb74a22907ca3a125d38e2201d58984092a6d859","tid":1095481,"uid":143288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"咁都忍得屎都食得<br />\n既然你屎都食得嘅 話你廢物都冇乜唔啱"},{"pid":"63f16d68bd9214487f0af22188355ad74c097aed","tid":1095481,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb74a22907ca3a125d38e2201d58984092a6d859","tid":1095481,"uid":143288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"咁都忍得屎都食得<br />\n既然你屎都食得嘅 話你廢物都冇乜唔啱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"真係太愛佢，我寧願忍佢氣"},{"pid":"3786d3224416c5ad062bd55ebd2d7e327f601fc1","tid":1095481,"uid":71096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"睇唔起你的女人一世都睇你唔起，你要繼續下去嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}